        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="关于黑夜模式按钮"><a href="#关于黑夜模式按钮" class="headerlink" title="关于黑夜模式按钮"></a>关于黑夜模式按钮</h2><p>参考资料<a href="https://nekodeng.gitee.io/posts/blog-night-mode.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nekodeng:关于给hexo博客适配全局深色模式</a></p><p>原文中的按钮是按博主本人的博客来适配的，我也只是针对我自己的博客做出了相应的修改。</p><p>在主题的layout.ejs文件中找到body标签的开始标签在后面加上这些js和html代码，这里我放的位置为：/layout/layout.ejs</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="actionscript">    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (localStorage.getItem(<span class="hljs-string">'dark'</span>) === <span class="hljs-string">'1'</span>) {</span><br><span class="javascript">    <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.body.classList.add(<span class="hljs-string">'dark'</span>);</span><br>    }<br><span class="javascript">    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">Date</span>().getHours() &gt;= <span class="hljs-number">22</span> || <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">Date</span>().getHours() &lt; <span class="hljs-number">7</span>) {</span><br><span class="javascript">    <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.body.classList.add(<span class="hljs-string">'dark'</span>);</span><br>    } <br><span class="actionscript">    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (matchMedia(<span class="hljs-string">'(prefers-color-scheme: dark)'</span>).matches) {</span><br><span class="javascript">    <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.body.classList.add(<span class="hljs-string">'dark'</span>);</span><br>    }<br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">onclick</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"switchNightMode()"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"sma"</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">i</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"fa fa-moon-o"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"nightMode"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">aria-hidden</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"true"</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">i</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>按钮的css样式，放到css文件里面，这里我放到的是source\css\matery.css</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css"><span class="hljs-comment">/* 深色模式按钮设置 */</span><br><span class="hljs-selector-id">#sma</span> {<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">background</span>: <span class="hljs-number">#000</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">38px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>: <span class="hljs-number">38px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">display</span>: block;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: fixed;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="hljs-number">50%</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">right</span>: <span class="hljs-number">15px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">bottom</span>: <span class="hljs-number">170px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">padding-top</span>: <span class="hljs-number">15px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">margin-bottom</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="hljs-number">998</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">cursor</span>: pointer;<br>}<br><br><span class="hljs-selector-id">#sma</span> <span class="hljs-selector-class">.fa-moon-o</span> {<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">right</span>: <span class="hljs-number">8px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">bottom</span>: <span class="hljs-number">8px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1.48rem</span><span class="hljs-meta">!important</span>;<br>}<br><span class="hljs-selector-id">#sma</span> <span class="hljs-selector-class">.fa-lightbulb-o</span>  {<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">position</span>: absolute;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">right</span>: <span class="hljs-number">13px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">bottom</span>: <span class="hljs-number">8px</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1.5rem</span><span class="hljs-meta">!important</span>;<br>}<br><br><span class="hljs-selector-class">.fa-moon-o</span><span class="hljs-selector-pseudo">:before</span> {<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">content</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"\f186"</span>;<br>}<br><span class="hljs-selector-class">.fa-comments</span><span class="hljs-selector-pseudo">:before</span> {<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">content</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"\f086"</span>;<br>}<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>CSS选择器覆盖样式代码，同样放到source\css\matery.css里面</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css"><span class="hljs-comment">/* 深色模式设置 */</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">/* 字体颜色变灰白色 */</span> <br><span class="hljs-selector-tag">body</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.dark</span> <span class="hljs-selector-class">.fas</span>,<br><span class="hljs-selector-tag">body</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.dark</span> <span class="hljs-selector-class">.title</span>,<br><span class="hljs-selector-tag">body</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.dark</span> <span class="hljs-selector-class">.row</span> <